---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Dashboard | LifeFlow</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --dash-bg: #0f172a;
        --dash-surface: #1e293b;
        --dash-border: #334155;
        --dash-text: #f1f5f9;
        --dash-text-dim: #94a3b8;
        --dash-accent: #3b82f6;
        --dash-green: #22c55e;
      }

      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

      body {
        font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
        background: var(--dash-bg);
        color: var(--dash-text);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .redirect-card {
        background: var(--dash-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--dash-border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 480px;
        width: 90%;
      }

      .redirect-card h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .redirect-card .logo-tf { color: var(--dash-accent); }
      .redirect-card .logo-lf { color: var(--dash-green); }

      .redirect-card p {
        color: var(--dash-text-dim);
        font-size: 0.9375rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .redirect-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
        background: var(--dash-accent);
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.9375rem;
        transition: opacity 0.2s;
      }

      .redirect-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

      .home-link {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        color: var(--dash-text-dim);
        font-size: 0.8125rem;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .home-link:hover { color: var(--dash-text); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="redirect-card">
      <h1>
        <span class="logo-tf">TechFlow</span> +
        <span class="logo-lf">LifeFlow</span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        LifeFlow 대시보드가 TechFlow 통합 대시보드로 이전되었습니다.<br />
        두 블로그의 통합 현황을 한곳에서 확인하세요.
      </p>
      <a href="https://ai-revenue-blog.vercel.app/dashboard/" class="redirect-btn">
        통합 대시보드로 이동
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="home-link">LifeFlow 블로그 홈으로</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
